 * As network admin role, i may first setup a network config through the operator dashboard, and then start the network;
 * As network admin role, with a running network, i may wanna add/remove an org into/from the consortium (optional);
 * As org admin role, with a running network, i may wanna start a new peer or new orderer node (for ordererOrg)

Welcome for comments.

